<subSubSection id="48D355CA8EAFFF2148F757B4FC29FF07" pageId="225" pageNumber="226" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="007606418EAFFF2148F757B4FC29FF07" blockId="225.[151,1436,151,248]" pageId="225" pageNumber="226">
<emphasis id="32BDDA538EAFFF2148F757B4FE9EFF40" bold="true" box="[199,315,152,176]" pageId="225" pageNumber="226">Remarks.</emphasis>
The following two genera are not quoted from the 
<collectingRegion id="C20DC8A38EAFFF214B4257BBFB85FF5F" box="[882,1056,151,175]" country="Democratic Republic of the Congo" name="Orientale" pageId="225" pageNumber="226">Oriental region</collectingRegion>
: 
<taxonomicName id="C7C97DC28EAFFF214C1A57B4FA39FF5F" authority="Ponomarenko, 1972" authorityName="Ponomarenko" authorityYear="1972" box="[1066,1436,151,176]" class="Insecta" family="Dryinidae" genus="Mirodryinus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="225" pageNumber="226" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="32BDDA538EAFFF214C1A57B4FB10FF40" box="[1066,1205,152,176]" italics="true" pageId="225" pageNumber="226">Mirodryinus</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="64587BB08EAFFF214C8B57BBFA39FF5F" author="Ponomarenko" box="[1211,1436,151,175]" firstAuthor="Ponomarenko" pageId="225" pageNumber="226" pagination="673 - 680" refId="ref368915" refString="Ponomarenko, N. G. (1972) [On the fauna of dryinids (Hymenoptera, Dryinidae) of the Mongolian People's Republic]. [Insects of Mongolia], 1, 673 - 680. (In Russian)." type="journal article" year="1972">Ponomarenko, 1972</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
(Palaearctic) and 
<taxonomicName id="C7C97DC28EAFFF2149435790FD66FF24" authority="Forster, 1856" authorityName="Forster" authorityYear="1856" box="[371,707,188,212]" class="Insecta" family="Dryinidae" genus="Mystrophorus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="225" pageNumber="226" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="32BDDA538EAFFF2149435790FDAAFF24" box="[371,527,188,212]" italics="true" pageId="225" pageNumber="226">Mystrophorus</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="64587BB08EAFFF214A125790FD66FF24" author="Forster" box="[546,707,188,212]" firstAuthor="Forster" pageId="225" pageNumber="226" refId="ref359146" refString="Forster, A. (1856) Hymenopterologischer Studien, 2. Chalcidiae und Proctotrupii. Ernst ter Meer, Aachen, 152 pp." type="book" year="1856">Förster, 1856</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
(Palaearctic). Larvae of 
<taxonomicName id="C7C97DC28EAFFF214C395790FB00FF24" authorityName="Forster" authorityYear="1856" box="[1033,1189,188,212]" class="Insecta" family="Dryinidae" genus="Mystrophorus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="225" pageNumber="226" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="32BDDA538EAFFF214C395790FB00FF24" box="[1033,1189,188,212]" italics="true" pageId="225" pageNumber="226">Mystrophorus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
were described by 
<bibRefCitation id="64587BB08EAFFF2148A757F3FE49FF07" author="Guglielmino &amp; Buckle" box="[151,492,223,247]" firstAuthor="Guglielmino" pageId="225" pageNumber="226" pagination="57 - 66" refId="ref359960" refString="Guglielmino, A. &amp; Buckle, C. (2010) Description of larval instars of Mystrophorus formicaeformis Ruthe (Hymenoptera: Dryinidae). Zootaxa, 2602, 57 - 66." type="journal article" year="2010">Guglielmino &amp; Bückle (2010)</bibRefCitation>
; larvae of 
<taxonomicName id="C7C97DC28EAFFF214A5257CCFD48FF08" authorityName="Ponomarenko" authorityYear="1972" box="[610,749,224,248]" class="Insecta" family="Dryinidae" genus="Mirodryinus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="225" pageNumber="226" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="32BDDA538EAFFF214A5257CCFD48FF08" box="[610,749,224,248]" italics="true" pageId="225" pageNumber="226">Mirodryinus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
are unknown.
</paragraph>
